{"tid":384042,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"美翻！「泰國結衣」臉小胸大還高學歷　網友驚呼戀愛啦","createTime":"2017-09-02T04:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T12:46:19.000Z","uid":31314,"like":61,"dislike":211,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebe16529b2a736f06f410f4c2424040c273ff081","tid":384042,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">曾經慘被網友評為「<strong>臉大胸小</strong></span>」代表的日本藝人新垣結衣，人氣並不因此受影響，現在更躍居當紅一線女星的地位！如今泰國出現了一名正妹模特兒May Sitapha，臉蛋竟然和新垣結衣有九分神似；帶著「天使臉孔」的她，甚至還擁有「魔鬼身材」，這樣反差的衝突，讓許多男性粉絲為之瘋狂，並將她封為「泰國結衣」。但May Sitapha可不是空有外表，她還是從日本名校早稻田大學畢業的，讓許多人驚呼，如此樣樣完美的她，實在是「太不科學啦！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/59a8fb77d5c09709beb9a0df_201709011417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F59a8fb77d5c09709beb9a0df_201709011417.jpg&h=04337f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/59a8fe5356b76509c43948ef_201709011429.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F59a8fe5356b76509c43948ef_201709011429.jpg&h=26a3b2dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/59a8fe5356b76509c43948ef_201709011429.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F59a8fe5356b76509c43948ef_201709011429.jpg&h=26a3b2dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMay Sitapha（圖）被網友封為泰國版的新垣結衣，2人神韻極為相似。<br />\n現年26歲的May Sitapha，家住泰國曼谷。早在就讀於早稻田大學時期，她就已是受到注目的校花，甚至還獲得日本媒體爭相報導，將她封為「最美的泰國女孩」。畢業後的May Sitapha，頂著高顏值且高學歷的光環，立刻投入廣告業擔任模特兒的工作，現在她的臉書及IG都有超過10萬名以上的粉絲追蹤，人氣可見一斑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/59a8fcae56b76509c43948e7_201709011422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F59a8fcae56b76509c43948e7_201709011422.jpg&h=f775d226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/59a8fceed5c09709beb9a0e1_201709011423.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F59a8fceed5c09709beb9a0e1_201709011423.jpg&h=1310329d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/59a8fd13d5c09709beb9a0e2_201709011424.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F59a8fd13d5c09709beb9a0e2_201709011424.jpg&h=802112e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMay Sitapha時常在臉書等社群網站上，分享自己的生活照、工作照與粉絲分享；除了拍美照之外，May Sitapha還不吝展現自己唱歌的才華，曾上傳自己翻唱他人歌曲的影片，廣受網友好評，讚她是真正的多才多藝女神。"},{"pid":"bd16cdeaa69b8bf675a5b80eb6e3271f47f9f704","tid":384042,"uid":2419,"like":175,"dislike":2,"score":173,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"仲有J添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b323bd3bb2589c27045f72dcc7fdf0d6d8274ad4","tid":384042,"uid":104035,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"幾靚, 可惜有j"},{"pid":"ea0841d08bff8516ceb9fb420eac858fe604b71d","tid":384042,"uid":104035,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"幾靚, 可惜有j"},{"pid":"e128fc89b4094d7792fd1790c886f75524c86c27","tid":384042,"uid":5946,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:12:48.000Z","msg":"有丁，不了。<br />\n不過想含下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcab7ffbd414a03620c27d2ecd4e079fcfadae1","tid":384042,"uid":141181,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:14:46.000Z","msg":"有J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7182e23552a3f938229eda52b44d9bd44f93ffb9","tid":384042,"uid":23592,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T